}

.ptr__children,
.ptr__pull-down {
  transition: transform 0.2s cubic-bezier(0, 0, 0.31, 1); }

.ptr__pull-down {
  position: absolute;
  overflow: hidden;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  top: 0;
  visibility: hidden; }
  .ptr__pull-down > div {
    display: none; }

    */

    display: none; }
  .ptr--dragging .ptr__pull-down--pull-more {

  .ptr--pull-down-treshold-breached .ptr__pull-down--loading {
